\\\"a52\\\">The following locations will be reduced to 0 Total capacity (Receipts and Deliveries) for the duration of the maintenance:&#160;</span></DIV><ul type=\\\"disc\\\" class=\\\"r16\\\"><DIV><li class=\\\"a53l\\\"><DIV class=\\\"a53p\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:700;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Corning - Empire (Loc prop 640167) </span></DIV></li></DIV></ul><DIV style=\\\"margin-top:10pt;padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\"><br/></span><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:700;text-decoration:underline;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">AutoPAL Availability</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">At this time, AutoPAL remains available.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">As a reminder to customers, the intent of the AutoPAL service is to utilize nominal quantities to resolve minor pool imbalances that result from small upstream or downstream reductions during the Gas Day. These quantities are then paid back the next cycle of the Gas Day.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">MPC will monitor AutoPAL activity and reserves the right to make AutoPAL unavailable.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">&#160;</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:700;text-decoration:underline;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">RCC’s</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Reservation Charge Credits will be determined per the process set forth in Section 15 of MPC’s FERC Gas tariff.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">&#160;</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:700;text-decoration:underline;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Questions</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">If you have questions, please contact Customer Services at 866-581-6487.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Please continue to monitor our Critical Notices for updates on progress as well.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:12.0pt;\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">&#160;</span></DIV></DIV></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></TD><TD WIDTH=\\\"100%\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"0\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH=\\\"0\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"100%\\\"></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></DIV></body></html>\"},\"startTime\":\"2026-04-21T13:29:06.0666957Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-21T13:29:06.543033Z\",\"trackingId\":\"d007340c-cf94-40b1-b0a5-988619cf01fe\",\"clientTrackingId\":\"08584248287496189935753873067CU00\",\"code\":\"OK\",\"status\":\"Succeeded\"},{\"name\":\"Call_Foundry_Extraction\",\"startTime\":\"2026-04-21T13:29:06.5715078Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-21T13:29:07.9900165Z\",\"trackingId\":\"7f4d327a-8d08-4a59-90b1-ad15e7579ef0\",\"clientTrackingId\":\"08584248287496189935753873067CU00\",\"code\":\"BadRequest\",\"status\":\"Failed\",\"error\":{\"code\":\"InvalidTemplate\",\"message\":\"Unable to process template language expressions in action 'Call_Foundry_Extraction' inputs at line '0' and column '0': 'The workflow parameter 'foundryApiKey' is not found.'.\"}},{\"name\":\"Parse_Foundry_Response\",\"startTime\":\"2026-04-21T13:29:07.9907405Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-21T13:29:07.9911017Z\",\"trackingId\":\"6de85331-531a-4cf4-9499-8